Thrifts and Mortgage Finance

Company Overview of Equity Financial Trust Company



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Equity Financial Trust Company provides alternative residential mortgage solutions for brokers and borrowers. The company offers mortgage solutions in the areas of self-business, bruised credit, and thin or no credit. It also provides online tools and resources for brokers to access the information, such as offers and incentives, events, originating documents, mortgage servicing documents, and others. In addition, the company offers deposit services that include guaranteed investment certificates. Equity Financial Trust Company was formerly known as Equity Transfer & Trust Company and changed its name to Equity Financial Trust Company in October 2010. The company was founded in 1990 and is b...
Equity Financial Trust Company provides alternative residential mortgage solutions for brokers and borrowers. The company offers mortgage solutions in the areas of self-business, bruised credit, and thin or no credit. It also provides online tools and resources for brokers to access the information, such as offers and incentives, events, originating documents, mortgage servicing documents, and others. In addition, the company offers deposit services that include guaranteed investment certificates. Equity Financial Trust Company was formerly known as Equity Transfer & Trust Company and changed its name to Equity Financial Trust Company in October 2010. The company was founded in 1990 and is based in Toronto, Canada. Equity Financial Trust Company operates as a subsidiary of Equity Financial Holdings Inc.
Detailed Description


P.O. Box 1160 Stn TDToronto, ON M5K 1P2CanadaFounded in 1990



