Equity Financial Trust Company Key Developments

Global Water Resources, Inc. Appoints as New Co-Transfer Agent & Registrar
Jul 29 16
Global Water Resources Inc. appointed Equity Financial Trust Company as new co-transfer agent & registrar in the City of Toronto.


GoldMoney Inc. Appoints Equity Financial Trust Company as Registrar and Transfer Agent
Apr 20 16
GoldMoney Inc. appointed Equity Financial Trust Company at its offices in Toronto, Ontario as registrar and transfer agent for the common shares.


