Careers
















We provide opportunities not obstacles.



 










Customer Centre
Equity Financial Trust Company offers alternative residential mortgage solutions tailored to your unique situation in securing a traditional prime residential mortgage. With an Ontario-wide network of mortgage brokers, you’ll find a trusted professional who’ll work closely with you to find the right solution for your mortgage needs.  Our mortgage brokers are fully licensed and have extensive experience and knowledge to help you secure the best mortgage for your personal or professional requirements.

 For a list of qualified mortgage brokers in Ontario, view our directory.



Mortgage Resources
Prepayment Calculator
Understanding Your Mortgage
Mortgage Service Documents






Business For Self
Do you own your own business?  Are you having difficulty finding financing for your home loan?  If you are a sole proprietor, in a partnership or are incorporated, Equity Financial Trust has flexible mortgage solutions specifically suited to your needs. We offer one to five (1-5) year terms with very competitive rates.


Bruised Credit
When life events play havoc with your mortgage needs  ̶  job loss, divorce, illness, etc.   ̶   you are not alone.  Equity Financial Trust is here to help you with alternative residential mortgage solutions that’ll get you back on your feet in no time.  Consult one of our mortgage brokers today and they’ll expertly structure a program with a mortgage solution designed to help you repair your credit quickly.


Thin or No Credit
Being new to the world of credit shouldn’t stop you from meeting your dreams of home ownership.  At Equity Financial Trust, our mortgage brokers know the challenges that you can face when securing a loan without a strong credit history. Contact our mortgage brokers to learn how you can be on the way to securing an alternative residential home mortgage today.





